text: "Witch's Game" is a single by American heavy metal band Cirith Ungol. It was released on a 12-inch record on April 24, 2020, with a live version of "Doomed Planet" as the B-side. It was the band's first record since their reunion in 2016, as well their first record since Paradise Lost in 1991. ==Track listing== ==References== Category:2020 singles Category:Cirith Ungol albums
title: Witch's Game
